---
title: Grilled Salmon, Cucumber and Apple Salad with Croutons and Creamy Dressing
description: This light, wholesome dinner will leave you feeling satisfied and energized! Grilled lemon-pepper salmon, crisp cucumber and apple and a creamy tzatziki dressing are the key to a delicious salad. Grab a fork and dig in!
